@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8317
@token = {{$dotenv AGENTSDK_PROXY_API_KEY}}
@token = {{$processEnv AGENTSDK_PROXY_API_KEY}}

### OpenAI Chat Completions API (OpenAI Protocol)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-5.5",
  "max_tokens": 1024,
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello! How are you?"
    }
  ]
}

### OpenAI List Models
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/models
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
